### Plotting results of structure analysis in O. novo-ulmi


### Plotting structure results for K = 3 on a map

simulate_point_locations.R	# script for simulating coordinates of labels so they do not overlap

requirements:
samples_locations.txt	# Coordinates of strain locations


plotStructureMap.R

requirements:
Pipie.R				# Script for plotting piecharts
world_intermediate.txt		# World map borders
samples_locations.txt		# Coordinates of strains
simulated_coords.txt		# Simulated coordinates of strain labels
k3.csv				# Results of structure



### Plotting strcuture barplots in O. novo-ulmi

